lead_paragraph: For five years, Chelsea were the nemesis of Arsenal and their coach Arsene Wenger so Saturday's resounding 3-0 victory in the London derby represented a psychological boost for the Frenchman.

headline.print_headline: Arsenal's Wenger Happy to Shed His Chelsea Hoodoo
headline.main: Arsenal's Wenger Happy to Shed His Chelsea Hoodoo
